article.description: — Isaiah Wilkins had 20 points with eight rebounds and four steals to lead Longwood to a 66-60 win over Gardner-Webb on Saturday.
article.headline: Wilkins has 20 points to lead Longwood past Gardner-Webb
article.linkText: Wilkins has 20 points to lead Longwood past Gardner-Webb
article.story: FARMVILLE, Va. -- — Isaiah Wilkins had 20 points with eight rebounds and four steals to lead Longwood to a 66-60 win over Gardner-Webb on Saturday. Zac Watson, Jordan Perkins and Nate Lliteras each scored nine points for the Lancers (10-5, 2-0 Big South Conference). Anthony Selden scored 17 points for the Bulldogs (9-8, 3-1). D'Maurian had 12 points and seven rebounds. Kareem Reid had 12 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25
